greatly appreciate the
outpouring of support.

06:36.600 --> 06:41.600 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Unfortunately, for my sparring
partners in Congress, I will
be back soon, so stand by."

06:43.533 --> 06:48.100 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
For the first time in the global
AIDS epidemic, more than half
of all those infected with

06:48.100 --> 06:51.366 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
HIV are on drugs
to treat the virus.

06:51.366 --> 06:56.366 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
A United Nations report today
also finds that overall AIDS
deaths have fallen to about half

06:57.333 --> 06:59.400 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
the level of 2005.

06:59.400 --> 07:04.400 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
The disease has killed
35 million people over
the past four decades.

07:06.333 --> 07:09.433 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
O.J. Simpson was granted
parole in Nevada today, after
nearly nine years in prison,

07:10.600 --> 07:13.033 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
and could be freed in October.

07:13.033 --> 07:18.033 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
