had been jailed for an armed
robbery in 2007 involving his

07:19.000 --> 07:21.133 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
own sports mementos.

07:21.133 --> 07:26.133 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
