hearing, Simpson, now 70 years
old, pleaded his case to the

07:27.000 --> 07:28.000 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
state parole board.

07:28.000 --> 07:29.266 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
O.J.

07:29.266 --> 07:31.266 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
SIMPSON, Inmate: I
have done my time.

07:31.266 --> 07:34.800 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
