wardens there, they will tell
you I have been -- I gave them

07:39.533 --> 07:40.533 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
my word.

07:40.533 --> 07:42.200 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
I believe in the jury system.

07:42.200 --> 07:44.166 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
I have honored their verdict.

07:44.166 --> 07:49.133 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Simpson's
defenders said that his 33-year
sentence was overly harsh, and

07:51.066 --> 07:54.633 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
