of his job, foreign policy
and domestic policy.

15:17.133 --> 15:19.066 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
And that's just simply
not going to be accepted.

15:19.066 --> 15:22.600 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
And so what is going to be
the answer if he objects?

15:22.600 --> 15:27.133 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
