a referral to the House of
Representatives for removal.

15:27.133 --> 15:30.466 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: For
removal of the president?

15:30.466 --> 15:31.466 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
WALTER DELLINGER: The
president, if I could just...

15:31.466 --> 15:33.533 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Of the president?

15:33.533 --> 15:37.533 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
