certainly be elements of
an obstruction of justice.

16:06.566 --> 16:08.900 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
DOUGLAS KMIEC: I think
that that is right.

16:08.900 --> 16:10.966 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Go ahead.

16:10.966 --> 16:13.700 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
